  "texts": [
    "Rationale: Phenobarbital induces hepatic metabolism of apixaban through CYP3A4, resulting in subtherapeutic plasma levels of apixaban and increasing risk of clinical failure. 7.",
    "DDI: Daptomycin / atorvastatin a.",
    "Clinical importance/relevance: Not important b.",
    "Rationale: There is an increased risk of skeletal muscle toxicity (i.e.",
    "rhabdomyolysis) when HMG-CoA Reductase inhibitors (statins) are administered concomitantly with daptomycin. 8."
  ]
